         </creditPoint>
      </credit>
   </about>
   <poem>
      <stanza stanzaNum="s1">
         <line lineNum="l1">Without substance there is</line>
         <line lineNum="l2">nothing. </line>
         <line lineNum="l3">The goal to be</line>
         <line lineNum="l4">barren, <keyword>void</keyword>.</line>
         <line lineNum="l5">It’s all I am, and</line>
         <line lineNum="l6">it’s what I desire.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza stanzaNum="s2">
         <line lineNum="l7">All for a</line>
         <line lineNum="l8">grave emptiness</line>
         <line lineNum="l9">in the core that</line>
         <line lineNum="l10">gives way to my</line>
         <line lineNum="l11">perfection.</line>
         <line lineNum="l12">I can feel the lining</line>
         <line lineNum="l13">inside twisting and</line>
         <line lineNum="l14">writhing in want for fodder,</line>
         <line lineNum="l15">a thrumming in the veins</line>
         <line lineNum="l16">echoing in the <keyword>vacancy</keyword>,</line>
         <line lineNum="l17">but I can’t let go now.</line>
         <line lineNum="l18">Not when I’m</line>
         <line lineNum="l19">so close.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza stanzaNum="s3">
         <line lineNum="l20">The <keyword>pain</keyword> is the proof.</line>
         <line lineNum="l21">Proof that it’s working,</line>
         <line lineNum="l22">that I’m <keyword>withering</keyword>, wasting</line>
         <line lineNum="l23">into sharpness and <keyword>pallidity</keyword>.</line>
         <line lineNum="l24">Bruising and <keyword>blood</keyword>-thinning,</line>
         <line lineNum="l25">a blueness under the eye,</line>
         <line lineNum="l26">the panging at the root,</line>
         <line lineNum="l27">the <keyword>wrongness</keyword> of it all —</line>
         <line lineNum="l28">it’s a vicious ecstasy.</line>
      </stanza>
      <stanza stanzaNum="s4">
         <line lineNum="l29">Ecstasy to be <keyword>hollow</keyword>.</line>
      </stanza>
   </poem>
</content>
